com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.api

Interface ISnomedRf2ImportService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SnomedRf2ImportService

    public interface ISnomedRf2ImportService
    Implementations allow importing SNOMED CT content from RF2 release archives.

      • getImportDetails

        ISnomedImportConfiguration getImportDetails(java.util.UUID importId)
        Retrieves the configuration object for the specified import run identifier.
        Parameters:
        importId - the identifier of the import run to look up

        the configuration object describing import details

      • startImport

        void startImport(java.util.UUID importId,
                 java.io.InputStream inputStream)
        Starts the import using the specified input stream.

        This method returns immediately. Import status can be followed by polling getImportDetails(UUID).

        Parameters:
        importId - the identifier of the import run to begin
        inputStream - the input stream opened on a valid RF2 release archive
        Throws:
        SnomedImportException - if the import can not start for some reason (import errors are only reflected in the import run's status flag)

      • create

        java.util.UUID create(ISnomedImportConfiguration configuration)
        Prepares a new SNOMED CT RF2 import run.
        Parameters:
        configuration - the configuration object for the import run to register
        Returns:
        the UUID of the associated configuration
        Throws:
        CodeSystemNotFoundException - if SNOMED CT as a code system is not registered
        CodeSystemVersionNotFoundException - if a code system version for SNOMED CT with the given identifier is not registered
        BadRequestException - if required properties on the configuration object are not populated
